{"tid":887453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐洲11豪門欲自組聯賽取代歐聯，全面壟斷電視轉播收益 | 體嘢報道】","createTime":"2018-11-03T02:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T18:51:49.000Z","uid":2169,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9726431612a77bf7892987586f66d946eb0c8329","tid":887453,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"【歐洲11豪門欲自組聯賽取代歐聯，全面壟斷電視轉播收益 | 體嘢報道】<br />\n<br />\n閱讀全文：<a href=\"https://wp.me/p75t7v-5k0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp75t7v-5k0&d=HkyGcFaseOEI6%2F2OHYoWKywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=db8a5af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wp.me/p75t7v-5k0</a><br />\n<br />\nFootball Leaks網站截獲一封電郵，發現以皇家馬德里、巴塞隆拿、拜仁慕尼黑、祖雲達斯為首的11家球會，密謀自行組建歐洲精英聯賽，全面壟斷電視轉播利益。有份參與計劃的，還有曼聯、車路士、利物浦、阿仙奴、曼城、PSG及AC米蘭。"},{"pid":"d7e25f5099f27df66815dc1235ecc7dc0038b0cd","tid":887453,"uid":54025,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"圍內打飛機聯賽"},{"pid":"ee9e1689cc8de3bd8e987a4ec5c688b33b6ee56e","tid":887453,"uid":111006,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"AC米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3dc8799c047c072a84c94e043fbfc6212c71c6","tid":887453,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee9e1689cc8de3bd8e987a4ec5c688b33b6ee56e","tid":887453,"uid":111006,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"AC米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d4e66889426673d922b4c8619ebf293585d4b9","tid":887453,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf3dc8799c047c072a84c94e043fbfc6212c71c6","tid":887453,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee9e1689cc8de3bd8e987a4ec5c688b33b6ee56e","tid":887453,"uid":